title: [Graendlor Pasture]
description: A broken, stony meadow slopes down before you towards a brush-lined creek.  Short, limby pines and modwirs line the ridgetop, and a shaded path wends its way towards a forested valley to the west.  A gentle breeze blows across the meadow, carrying the distinct smell of the roltons and gaks that call this pasture home.
paths: Obvious paths: northeast, southeast, west, northwest
